Basically, the size of your mana pool will become very important.  The Trial of Execution taxes the mana pool of enchanters.<br>
<br>
The stats as I find them in order of importance (from items)....<br>
<br>
- +Int (up to the cap)<br>
- +Mana<br>
- +Cha<br>
- +Resists<br>
<br>
