are you sure on the effect of CHR on Charm?  don't get me wrong, i am personally an advocate of high charisma and believe that it does effect charms.  however, i do not believe that Sony has ever officially confirmed that theory and i also recall reading inconclusive test results.  <br>
<br>
basically, there are two &quot;camps&quot; of chanter - those who think CHR is important post 120+ and those who do not.  i fall into the first camp, but know that there are strong believers in the second camp who i also consider to be quite knowledgeable chanters. <br>
<br>
and i wholeheartedly agree on the stamina call.  stamina and dex are both important stats for high level chanters.  <p><center>
